La pinicla cuenta la estória de un jovin pequeñu çorru llamau Vuk (Vic ena version ingresa), que empresas fuera de la madriguera de el su familia i, encima de el su regresu, aprende de el su tiu Karak que toda el su familia ha sidu disparu i muertu por un caça umanu. Karak then offers for Vuk to stay with him, i Karak continues to raise Vuk.

As Vuk grows older, he develops much cunning i cleverness. Now a young adult çorru, he finds a vixen llamau Foxy held captive en a cage on a human farm. He tricks the guard dogs i other animals, as well as the hunter himself, i eventually helps the vixen escape.

She joins Vuk i Karak in the woods, but Vuk's uncle es shot by humans during a hunt. Vuk swears revenge on the hunter i finally accomplishes it, playing many jokes on the hunter's dim-witted dogs i eventually on the man himself. Al final de la pinicla, Vuk i el su wife have cubs of their own.

